{"route":{"route":"/posts/5938ae8c/","outputPath":"posts/5938ae8c/index.html","kind":"post","title":"nodejs异步回调函数","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"5938ae8c"}},"description":"研究了一下javascript的异步回调函数,本来想像golang那样使用chan可以返回原始值,不过貌似无法做到,最后止步async/await,差不多就是用Promise的resolve返回值然后用await调用,不过await必须使用在async的函数里,局限还是有的. 如果使用非async的函数调用,返回的依旧","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/nodejs异步回调函数.md","route":"/posts/5938ae8c/","abbrlink":"5938ae8c","title":"nodejs异步回调函数","date":"2019-08-30 22:45:20","updated":"2019-08-30 22:45:20","tags":["nodejs"],"categories":["nodejs"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<p>研究了一下javascript的异步回调函数,本来想像golang那样使用chan可以返回原始值,不过貌似无法做到,最后止步async/await,差不多就是用Promise的resolve返回值然后用await调用,不过await必须使用在async的函数里,局限还是有的.<br>\n如果使用非async的函数调用,返回的依旧是Promise类型,需要使用.then.</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Promise</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"hljs-params\">resolve, reject</span>) {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">resolve</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test&quot;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    })</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test2</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>){</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>())</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test2</span>()</span></span></code></pre>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"5938ae8c","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}